        h1 &lsquo;Tawba Walk
        h3 An Arts and Music Festival
        .copy
          p.
            The 'Tawba Walk Arts & Music Festival is back in action and bigger than
            ever before! Mark your calendars and get ready for an all-local experience
            unlike any other as we feature the area's top artists, bands, performance
            groups, food trucks, microbreweries, and much more!
        #recap-video
          iframe(src='//www.youtube.com/embed/EzsuLH0YolA', frameborder='0', allowfullscreen)
        .copy
          p.
            Join us on Saturday, May 17th from 2-8 pm in Old Town Cornelius for a
            one-of-a-kind, community-inspired street festival that is sure to leave
            you feelin' a whole lotta love! The 'Tawba Walk is your all-access pass to
            discovering the top talent right here in your hometown while enjoying
            community as it should be. There will be fun for the whole entire family
            so bring the kids, your neighbors, and even your furry friends out to the
            event that's got everyone talking.... 'Tawba Walk VII!
